# Smart Traffic Prediction & Congestion Management System

The **Smart Traffic Prediction & Congestion Management System** is an AI-powered web application developed to analyze traffic conditions, predict congestion levels using Machine Learning, and provide traffic insights through an interactive dashboard. The system helps users understand traffic patterns and supports smarter transportation planning.

---

Project Objective

The objective of this project is to build an intelligent traffic management system that can:

- Analyze traffic data collected from different areas.
- Predict traffic congestion using Machine Learning.
- Display traffic information through an interactive dashboard.
- Help users understand traffic conditions for better travel planning.
- Provide a scalable foundation for future smart city traffic solutions.

---

Work Completed

1. Project Initialization
- Created project structure
- Initialized Git repository
- Uploaded project to GitHub
- Configured frontend and backend

---

2. Frontend Development
- Developed the application using React.js
- Created responsive UI
- Implemented:
  - Home Page
  - Login Page
  - Registration Page
  - User Dashboard
  - Navbar
  - Footer
- Connected frontend with backend APIs using Axios

---

3. Backend Development
- Developed REST APIs using FastAPI
- Organized backend into:
  - Routes
  - Services
  - Schemas
  - Utilities
- Configured CORS
- Implemented modular project architecture

---

4. User Authentication
Implemented secure authentication using MongoDB.

Features:
- User Registration
- User Login
- Password Hashing
- JWT Authentication
- Role-Based Access (Admin & Traffic Operator)

---

5. MongoDB Integration
- Connected FastAPI with MongoDB
- Created Users collection
- Imported Bangalore Traffic Dataset into MongoDB
- Successfully stored **8936 traffic records**

---

6. Dataset Exploration (EDA)
Performed Exploratory Data Analysis using Pandas.

Completed:
- Dataset inspection
- Missing value analysis
- Duplicate value checking
- Statistical summary
- Column analysis

Generated graphs for:
- Traffic Volume by Area
- Average Speed Distribution
- Congestion Level Distribution

---

7. Data Preprocessing
Performed preprocessing before model training.

Completed:
- Converted Date into Year, Month and Day
- Encoded categorical columns
- Prepared dataset for Machine Learning

---

8. Machine Learning Model
Developed a congestion prediction model using **Random Forest Regressor**.

Completed:
- Train-Test Split
- Model Training
- Model Evaluation
- Saved trained model (`traffic_model.pkl`)
- Saved Label Encoders (`label_encoders.pkl`)

---

9. Traffic APIs

Implemented APIs for:

### Authentication
- Register User
- Login User

### Traffic Module
- Fetch Available Areas
- Fetch Area Details

### Prediction Module
- Predict Traffic Congestion

All APIs were successfully tested using Swagger UI.

---

10. Dashboard Features

Implemented an interactive dashboard with:

- Total Areas
- Total Dataset Records
- AI Model Information
- Database Status
- Area Selection Dropdown
- Traffic Details Display
- AI-Based Congestion Prediction

